title: Joe's Farm Grill
typeOfFood: Lacto, American, Pizza, Italian, Thai, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Accommodating to vegans in that many vegetarian items can be made vegan upon request. Offers portobello mushroom salads, veggie pizza that can go cheeseless, sweet potato fries, among other options. Most of the vegetables are grown on the restaurant farm and are fresh and seasonal. Website has an extensive food allergies page.
